{"word":"Eliakim","slug":"eliakim","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Eliakim</b> <a href=\"#/H471\">H471</a> <br/> 1. Son of Melea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=30'>Luk 3:30</a><br/> 2. Son of Hilkiah, deputy of Hezekiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=18&verse=18'>2Ki 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=19&verse=2'>2Ki 19:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=36&verse=3'>Isa 36:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=36&verse=11'>Isa 36:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=36&verse=22'>Isa 36:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=37&verse=2'>Isa 37:2</a><br/> 3. Original name of Jehoiakim, king of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=34'>2Ki 23:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=4'>2Ch 36:4</a><br/> 4. Son of Abiud<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=13'>Mat 1:13</a> <br/> - Probably same as Shechaniah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=21'>1Ch 3:21</a> <br/> 5. A priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=41'>Neh 12:41</a>"}]}